","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"24 g","calories":"870 kJ \/ 208 kcal"},"usefulItems":"square baking pan (8 in. x 8 in.), parchment paper, refrigerator","hintsAndTricks":["Make your own Nutella® following the recipe for Chocolate Hazelnut Spread in The Basic Cookbook."],"basicInfo":["easy","15m","30m","36 portions"]}